			"label": "Create Todo Migration",
			"type": "shell",
			"command": "Remove-Item -Recurse -Force \"D:\\開發中\\worklog\\src\\WorkLog.Infrastructure\\Data\\Migrations\" -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue; dotnet ef migrations add AddTodoFeature -p \"D:\\開發中\\worklog\\src\\WorkLog.Infrastructure\\WorkLog.Infrastructure.csproj\" -s \"D:\\開發中\\worklog\\src\\WorkLog.Api\\WorkLog.Api.csproj\" -o Data/Migrations"
